{"tid":1186417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡漢月台竄逃…2女高中狂追　「伸腿救援」網讚帥翻追　大叔看不下","createTime":"2019-06-05T02:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T04:19:46.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"306ecd702f4e1c27219f5c9f28aa210f0d2d8ec8","tid":1186417,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"記者林瑩真／編譯<br />\n<br />\n日本日前發生一起癡漢騷擾女高中生事件，當女高中生們氣憤的追著癡漢時，一名大叔神<br />\n救援，直接伸腳絆倒癡漢。影片吸引大量網友討論及轉發，「癡漢就是噁心！」 <br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，在5月27日的上班、上課時間，一段影片在推特爆紅，引起瘋狂轉發。一<br />\n名男子奔馳於JR赤羽駅5-6號月台上，後面則有2名女高中生拼命追趕，更不時大喊「不要<br />\n跑！」讓其他乘客傻眼目睹。 <br />\n<br />\n所幸，一名大叔很快就反應過來，在男子跑過自己前面時，直接伸出腿絆倒男子，讓男子<br />\n在樓梯口前飛撲撞地，甚至還不小心滑了一下，因為這一腿，讓女高中生趕上男子，順利<br />\n抓到人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4142/d4142281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4142%2Fd4142281.jpg&h=f20c004f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/influencer_com_/status/1133140922022023168/video/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Finfluencer_com_%2Fstatus%2F1133140922022023168%2Fvideo%2F1&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLzHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=c3303dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Finfluencer_com_%2Fstatus%2F1133140922022023168%2Fvideo%2F1&h=9f957eea\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/influencer_com_/status/1133140922022023168/video/1</a>"},{"pid":"107d13adb711d03580993fc5053435d645cbcd30","tid":1186417,"uid":173617,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:22:10.000Z","msg":"日本好多mk妹呃錢，扮被非禮"},{"pid":"021c1470ef67d4f82e15b2971e93b6a2f1eae83b","tid":1186417,"uid":46911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAtgYCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAtgYCV.png&h=63f5e9dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1747fb0f3e9fda479a7c576fbe0